      <title>厄瓜多尔遭遇 60 年来最严重干旱 提前停电</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/ecuador-begins-power-cuts-early-amid-worst-drought-in-60-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于遭遇创纪录的干旱，厄瓜多尔本周原计划在夜间实施的轮流停电被提前到白天。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/ecuador-begins-power-cuts-early-amid-worst-drought-in-60-years</guid>
