    <item>
      <title>罗马尼亚预算修订后面临欧盟最大赤字</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/romania-faces-the-eu-s-widest-deficit-after-budget-revision</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗马尼亚政府在今年大选和总统选举之前提高了预算赤字目标，这是对欧盟财政规则的最新挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/romania-faces-the-eu-s-widest-deficit-after-budget-revision</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 13:51:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行观察家对自民党选举的关注点集中在一位候选人身上</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/boj-watchers-focus-on-ldp-election-comes-down-to-one-candidate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行观察人士正密切关注该国执政党自民党领导人选举，以了解其对货币政策前景的潜在影响，并将注意力集中在强烈主张维持宽松立场的人身上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/boj-watchers-focus-on-ldp-election-comes-down-to-one-candidate</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 13:11:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登政府提议禁止中国、俄罗斯汽车零部件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/biden-administration-proposes-ban-of-chinese-russian-car-parts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府提议制定一项规则，禁止销售和进口中国和俄罗斯制造的车联网硬件和软件，此举可能会增强美国抵御商务部所称“非常真实”的黑客威胁的安全。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/biden-administration-proposes-ban-of-chinese-russian-car-parts</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 12:45:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>律师要求南苏丹最高法院裁定投票延迟违法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/lawyers-ask-south-sudan-top-court-to-declare-vote-delay-illegal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南苏丹的一群律师对政府将原定于 12 月举行的选举推迟两年的决定提出质疑，他们认为此举违反宪法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/lawyers-ask-south-sudan-top-court-to-declare-vote-delay-illegal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 12:38:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国护士在里夫斯的会议演讲中拒绝加薪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/uk-nurses-reject-pay-offer-during-reeves-s-conference-speech</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯 (Rachel Reeves) 在工党年度会议上发表演讲庆祝她任内公共部门工资上涨帮助结束持续数月的罢工行动之时，英国最大的护士工会却拒绝了政府的加薪提议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/uk-nurses-reject-pay-offer-during-reeves-s-conference-speech</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 12:27:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>里夫斯承诺下个月在英国预算中展现“真正的雄心”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/rachel-reeves-promises-real-ambition-in-uk-budget-next-month</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯承诺下个月将提交一份展现“真正雄心”的英国预算，并在工党年度会议上发表演讲，为国家描绘积极的愿景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/rachel-reeves-promises-real-ambition-in-uk-budget-next-month</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 11:35:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>意大利预算因 Meloni 下调 2023 年债务而增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/meloni-gets-italian-budget-boost-with-2023-debt-revised-down</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利数据经过多年修订后，其债务比率降低了近三个百分点，这为意大利总理乔治亚·梅洛尼政府在准备公布新的预算目标时提供了助力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/meloni-gets-italian-budget-boost-with-2023-debt-revised-down</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 08:38:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员评估新内阁，法国市场债券风险上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/france-s-yield-premium-over-germany-rises-to-most-since-august</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者权衡法国总理米歇尔·巴尼耶（Michel Barnier）新内阁所面临的挑战及其控制国家巨额赤字的能力，法国政府债券表现落后于其他债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/france-s-yield-premium-over-germany-rises-to-most-since-august</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 08:31:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列空袭黎巴嫩造成 180 人死亡，冲突不断升级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/israel-steps-up-attacks-on-hezbollah-targets-in-south-lebanon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当地政府称，以色列周一对黎巴嫩南部真主党目标进行空袭，造成 180 多人死亡，双方敌对情绪不断升级，引发国际社会对爆发全面战争的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/israel-steps-up-attacks-on-hezbollah-targets-in-south-lebanon</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 06:01:15 GMT</pubDate>
